<br>
Anyhow, I saw something somewhere that Moodoro wanders somewhere that even evil races can reach him.  Does anyone know if he goes anywhere out of sight of the guards so I can give him gold without getting whacked?  Last time I went into Crow's they jumped me in there too, although that was about 10 levels ago.  <br>
<br>
Also, do you have to have good faction with Moodoro to give him the gold and get the card and book?<br>
<br>
